channel.title: Do you think the "satanic" backmasking of Stairway to Heaven is real?
channel.description:
Do you guys think in the song stairway to heaven by led zeppelin truely meant to have the satanic words if you play the song backwards? I mean like I'm sort of half and half right now. You tell me...
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BcL---4xQYA (fast forward to 4:21)
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WQaMU7FnrGU (backwards - fast forward to 1:27)
